## 10. Project Conventions

**Path alias** – Use `@/` for imports: `@/components/Button`, `@/services/api/client`, `@/constants/colors`. Configure in `tsconfig.json` and `babel.config.js` (babel-plugin-module-resolver).

**Barrel imports** – Avoid `index.ts` re-exports that pull in unused code. Import directly from source for tree shaking: `import { Button } from '@/components/ui/Button'` not `import { Button } from '@/components'`.

**Platform extensions** – Use `.ios.tsx`, `.android.tsx`, or `.native.ts` for platform-specific code. Expo picks the right file at build time.

```text
components/
  KeyboardAvoidingView.ios.tsx
  KeyboardAvoidingView.android.tsx
```

